---
title: Double One-Pot Spanish-Style Chorizo Rice with Parsley
description: This Spanish-style rice dish is packed full of goodness, with a rich tomato base, smokey chorizo and tender veggies. It’s a true one-pot wonder, all it needs is a little bit of time to let the magic happen!

